Looking at your code: https://github.com/espruino/EspruinoDocs/blob/0a349f329c566b0147377737cc54704aa61294f5/devices/TM1640.js#L24
c and d are normally high, and when you call sendCommand the waveform looks like:
d(0)
// i=0
c(0)
d(bit0)
c(1)
// i=1
c(0)
d(bit1)
c(1)
// ...
